nodes.text: Feydu was a Evocii male warrior who, during the Galactic War, was aboard the Galactic Republic's Valor-class cruiser Gav Daragon.

Evocii Avenger Feydu was added to the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic in Game Update 2.2, as a Nightmare Force Vendor for Operation: Scum and Villainy, though he was later removed in a reorganizing of endgame gear.
